If you like meats, cheeses, beer, and wine, welcome to heaven. Every crostini and panini on yen menu -- including the brunch ones -- are worth a try. If you're dining in, you'll always find a knowledgeable and helpful staff. An if you're ordering for delivery (you'll have to call; they're not on Seamless), you're in for speedy and accurate delivery. Protip: Share the crostini pupu platter. Five squares at a discounted price for a greater variety of deliciousness!
